                    <h2>How will City, University of London help me achieve my career goals?</h2>
                    <p>Every course at City, University of London is dynamic, relevant and informed by high-quality academic research – and your modules will be taught by academic professors with industry experience.</p>
<p>Located in London’s business and financial district, the University has close links with key business players in the City and beyond – so you’ll be perfectly placed to secure an internship, work placement or job once you’ve graduated. The area is home to hundreds of global companies, including:</p>
<ul>
<li>Google</li>
<li>Charterhouse Capital Partners</li>
<li>Deloitte</li>
<li>Lloyds Banking Group</li>
<li>Amazon</li>
</ul>
<p>Find out more about living in the City of London in our <a href="https://www.intostudy.com/en/universities/city-university-london/living-in-city-of-london">student city guide</a>.</p>

