                    <h2>What are the facilities like at City, University of London?</h2>
                    <p>Each of City’s five Schools has its own academic department, research centre and subject-specific facilities. Depending on your degree, you could study at:</p>
<ul>
<li>The School of Arts and Social Sciences</li>
<li>The School of Health Sciences</li>
<li>The School of Mathematics, Computer Science and Engineering</li>
<li>The City Law School</li>
<li>The Business School (formerly Cass)</li>
</ul>
<p>From the Financial Resources Suite at the Business School to the Handley Page Laboratory at the School of Mathematics, Computer Science and Engineering, there are excellent specialist facilities to support your learning.</p>

